$pearl_page_medicall["about-us"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1497433933872{margin-top: -60px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-image: url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/medicall/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2017/06/about_us.jpg?id=1293) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_class="sm_mgt_0"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1496906021767{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}"]<span style="color: #ffffff;"><a style="color: #ffffff;" href="/medicall">Home</a> / About US</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="About us" font_container="tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes" css=".vc_custom_1496906086450{margin-bottom: 140px !important;}"][vc_column_text] <p style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 44px;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">We believe that everyone can have a healthy smile for life and with our help it’s easier than you think! We are passionate about helping patients to live better quality lives thanks to good oral health.</span></p> [/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="Jane Jackson " font_container="tag:h4|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_custom_heading text="Dentist" font_container="tag:h5|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff" use_theme_fonts="yes"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column offset="vc_col-lg-9 vc_col-md-9 vc_col-xs-12"][vc_custom_heading text="Why Choose Us?" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]Our conscience can’t rest so long as 37 million Americans are poor and forgotten by their leaders in Washington and by the media elites. And we cannot ignore the very real concerns of Americans who are not worried about illegal immigration because they are racist or xenophobic, but because they fear it will result in lower wages when they’re already struggling to raise their families. We shouldn’t use the obstacles we face as an excuse for cynicism.[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text="Certificates of completion" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][stm_carousel_gallery images_effect="0" images_qty="4" images_margin="30" navigation="disable" thumbnails="disable" description="disable" pagination="disable" images="1290,1287,1285,62,61" image_size="190x140" css=".vc_custom_1496923385417{margin-top: 30px !important;}"][vc_custom_heading text="Our mission" font_container="tag:h3|text_align:left" use_theme_fonts="yes"][vc_column_text]For we have a choice in this country. Kennedy called our “intellectual and moral strength.” Yes, government must lead on energy independence, but each of us must do our part to make our homes and businesses more efficient. That is why there is a mosque in every state of our union, and over 1,200 mosques within our borders. To play a role in fulfilling Palestinian aspirations, and to unify the Palestinian people, Hamas must put an end to violence, recognize past agreements, and recognize Israel’s right to exist.[/vc_column_text][stm_iconlist icon="stmicon-checkmark-circle" margins="15"] <ul> <li>The first thing you must do is go to the dentist. Not just every now and again when something hurts or breaks but on a regular basis. Once or twice a year is a minimum. My regular patients rarely have major disasters.</li> <li>People neglect their teeth for all sorts of reasons. While cost is often given as the reason, fear, time and embarrassment are just as common.</li> <li>Bad teeth are embarrassing for many people. Over the years I have watched people get a new lease on life from having a smile make-over.</li> </ul> [/stm_iconlist][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" offset="vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3 vc_hidden-sm vc_col-xs-12 vc_hidden-xs"][stm_sidebar sidebar="1165"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" el_class="mbc" css=".vc_custom_1496924638675{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: -60px !important;}"][vc_column][stm_cta button_color="white" button_icon_pos="" link="url:%2Fmedicall%2Fcontacts|title:Contact%20us||" css=".vc_custom_1501680758242{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}"] <h4><span style="color: #ffffff;">Looking for a good and affordable doctor in your town?</span></h4> [/stm_cta][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1501736521:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wp_page_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'center', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h1', ), 'stm_sidebar_position' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), '_wpb_shortcodes_custom_css' => array ( 0 => '.vc_custom_1497433933872{margin-top: -60px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-image: url(http://pearl.stylemixthemes.com/medicall/wp-content/uploads/sites/6/2017/06/about_us.jpg?id=1293) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}.vc_custom_1496924638675{margin-top: 50px !important;margin-bottom: -60px !important;}.vc_custom_1496906021767{margin-bottom: 15px !important;}.vc_custom_1496906086450{margin-bottom: 140px !important;}.vc_custom_1496923385417{margin-top: 30px !important;}.vc_custom_1501680758242{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 30px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}', ), ), );
$pearl_page_medicall["meet-the-team"] = array ( 'content' => '[vc_row][vc_column][stm_staff_container style="style_5"][stm_staff name="Grace Taylor" image="1336" image_size="175x175" job="Associate Otolaryngologist" facebook="#" twitter="#" description="Dr Grace Taylor joined the team at The Dental Clinic in early 2006. Being a member of a large private practice that specialises in implant and cosmetic dentistry has been a great way for Dr Ann Taylor to increase her knowledge and experience in all areas of dentistry. Being a general dentist, Dr Grace Taylor has found it easy to diagnose orthodontic problems in children early, as they come in for their regular preventative checks." full_description="Dr Grace Taylor has a keen interest in Orthodontics and has completed further studies in this field in order to offer her patients a broader range of treatment. Being a general dentist, Dr Grace Taylor has found it easy to diagnose orthodontic problems in children early, as they come in for their regular preventative checks. This early diagnosis often leads to an easier course of orthodontics for children and teenagers. Having completed Invisalign training and lingual braces, Dr Grace Taylor can offer many aesthetic options to adults who tend to prefer these over traditional braces for aesthetic reasons."][stm_staff name="Robert Henderson" image="1337" image_size="175x175" job="Oral Health Therapist" facebook="#" twitter="#" insta="#" description="Dr Robert Henderson was born in Berlin and educated at Trinity School. He graduated from the University of Munich in 1985. Shortly after graduation he was one of 3 new graduates to be accepted into a pilot intern and registrar program at the newly opened Dental Hospital. During his 3 years at Hospital, Dr Robert Henderson was able to gain invaluable experience in treating thousands of patients who had been neglected by the health system. This included general dentistry, emergency care, trauma, oral surgery and orthodontics." full_description="In 1984, he accepted a position at San Diego Dental Hospital in the department of Orthodontics. While this provided valuable training Dr Robert Henderson decided his career was in general practice and joined the practice of Dr William Bale in Tokyo. At the beginning of 1995 he took over as principal. Dr Robert Henderson qualified from Liverpool in 2008 and did his vocational training at Windsor Dental Practice. Having completed his training, he has worked here since as an associate and is now a vocational trainer himself."][stm_staff name="Jane Jackson" image="1338" image_size="175x175" job="Practice Manager" facebook="#" twitter="#" linkedin="#" description="Jane Jackson has been with the practice for over 25 years and is the glue that keeps the practice together! After a 6 month stint working for Bank, Jane Jackson decided the banking career was not for her and joined a local dentist as a junior Dental Assistant with very little experience. Her journey began on working her way through all aspects of the practice giving her the knowledge and understanding of the nuts and bolts of the practice." full_description="Jane Jackson quickly decided that she could run the practice better than Glenn and her journey began on working her way through all aspects of the practice giving her the knowledge and understanding of the nuts and bolts of the practice. Jane Jackson is responsible for the overall successful organisation and running of the practice, ensuring that the standards of the practice are upheld. Responsible for the business administration and staffing of the practice. Outside of work, Jane’s focus is on her family and being mum to her two beautiful daughters Anna and Julia. She also loves to travel, having travelled to Europe twice before having a family. Now travel tends to be smaller family holidays."][stm_staff name="Robert Henderson" image="1335" image_size="175x175" job="Practice Principal" facebook="#" twitter="#" description="Robert graduated from the University of QLD in 2005 with a Bachelor of Applied Science (Oral Health). From there he worked in the small towns of Yeppoon and Rockhampton doing a combination of private practice and school dental therapy. Robert opted for the dental field as he has always had a keen interest in health and wanted to help people better their oral health and keep their teeth for life." full_description="In 2010, Robert moved to Sydney and officially accepted his position at the practice in early 2011. Robert opted for the dental field as he has always had a keen interest in health and wanted to help people better their oral health and keep their teeth for life. When not in work, Robert has a keen interest in floristry and photography. Robert is currently on maternity leave following the birth of his darling daughter Bella and is enjoying the precious time with her new little family!"][stm_staff name="Ann Taylor" image="1340" image_size="175x175" job="Associate Otolaryngologist" facebook="#" twitter="#" description="Dr Ann Taylor joined the team at The Dental Clinic in early 2006. Being a member of a large private practice that specialises in implant and cosmetic dentistry has been a great way for Dr Ann Taylor to increase her knowledge and experience in all areas of dentistry. Being a general dentist, Dr Ann Taylor has found it easy to diagnose orthodontic problems in children early, as they come in for their regular preventative checks." full_description="Dr Ann Taylor has a keen interest in Orthodontics and has completed further studies in this field in order to offer her patients a broader range of treatment. Being a general dentist, Dr Ann Taylor has found it easy to diagnose orthodontic problems in children early, as they come in for their regular preventative checks. This early diagnosis often leads to an easier course of orthodontics for children and teenagers. Having completed Invisalign training and lingual braces, Dr Ann Taylor can offer many aesthetic options to adults who tend to prefer these over traditional braces for aesthetic reasons."][stm_staff name="Sofie Hagen" image="1339" image_size="175x175" job="Pediatric Dentist" facebook="#" twitter="#" description="Dr Sofie Hagen qualified from Liverpool in 2008 and did his vocational training at Windsor Dental Practice. Having completed his training, he has worked here since as an associate and is now a vocational trainer himself. Sofie Hagen has good experience with treating patients in pain, having worked the out-of-hours services in Salford and Oldham since 2006. He is very good with dealing with patients who are nervous. Having completed his training, he has worked here since." full_description="Sofie Hagen has good experience with treating patients in pain, having worked the out-of-hours services in Salford and Oldham since 2006. He is very good with dealing with patients who are nervous. Having completed his training, he has worked here since."][/stm_staff_container][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'meta' => array ( '_vc_post_settings' => array ( 0 => 'a:1:{s:10:"vc_grid_id";a:0:{}}', ), '_edit_lock' => array ( 0 => '1501763049:1', ), '_edit_last' => array ( 0 => '1', ), '_wp_page_template' => array ( 0 => 'default', ), '_wpb_vc_js_status' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_breadcrumbs' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box' => array ( 0 => 'true', ), 'page_title_box_align' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_title_size' => array ( 0 => 'h1', ), 'stm_sidebar_position' => array ( 0 => 'left', ), 'page_title_box_text_color' => array ( 0 => 'ffffff', ), 'page_title_box_bg_image' => array ( 0 => '708', ), ), );
